text: Christian Gödl (born 17 March 1980) is an Austrian professional darts player who plays in Professional Darts Corporation events. He made his PDC European Tour debut in the 2018 German Darts Grand Prix, but was whitewashed 6–0 by Stephen Bunting. Gödl has also qualified for the 2019 Austrian Darts Championship. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian darts players
